# Lumi App Flow — Audio-First Reset

## Pages

1️⃣ Landing Page  
- Basic intro text
- Login / Signup

2️⃣ Journal Page  
- Large Start Conversation button (centered)
- Conversation log below button

---

## Conversation Loop

- User clicks Start Conversation
- Lumi speaks (ElevenLabs)
- User responds (Mic)
- Transcription → GPT-4o → Response
- Loop continues until end of session
- Conversation stored, persona_state updated

---

## Roles

- User: Journaling participant
- Developer: Access to persona_state for tuning
- No admin panel required

